th / taskhelp                 Shows help for a task
 
   Format:
      ;th <task>              Shows help for the <task>
 
   Notes:
      <task> can be any Axmud built-in or external task.
      <task> can be in the form of a task's label (e.g. 'stat, 'status'), its
         formal name (e.g. 'status_task') or the unique name of a currently-
         running task (e.g. 'status_task_4').
      (Use the ';listtasklabel' command to list all task labels.)
 
   User commands:
      th / thelp / taskhelp
